<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Q&A</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="http://localhost:3000/css/QA_wep.css">
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <% include ./header %>
    </header>
    <section class="background1">
        <br><br><br><br>
        <div class="QA_title">Q&A</div><br><br>
        <div class="intro">앱앤미와 관련되어 궁금한 점이 있다면<br> 질문하고 궁금증을 풀어보세요. </div><br><br><br>
        <hr width="1200px" color="gray" size="1"><br><br><br><br>
        <center>
            <form action="/addBoard" method="post">
                <table width="1000px" class="list-table">
                    <tr height="40px">
                        <td style="background-color:#E4E4E4; ">제목</td>
                        <td><input type="text" name="title" size="50" style="float:left; margin-left: 1%; width: 400px; height:30px" placeholder="제목을 입력해 주세요."></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr height="40px">
                        <td style="background-color:#E4E4E4; ">작성자</td>
                        <td><input type="text" name="name" size="50" style="float:left;  margin-left:1%; width: 400px; height:30px" placeholder="실명을 입력해주세요."></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr height="40px">
                        <td colspan="2"><textarea name="content" style="float:left;  margin-left:0.5%; margin-top: 0.5%; margin-bottom:0.5%;" cols="130" rows="17" placeholder="내용을 입력해주세요."></textarea></td>

                </table>
                <input type="image" src="http://localhost:3000/img/O.jpg" alt="Submit Form" style="float: right; margin-right:11%; margin-top:1.5%; border: 0px;" />
                <a href="qa"><img style="float: right; margin-right:1%; margin-top:1.5%;" src="http://localhost:3000/img/X.jpg"></a>
            </form>
        </center>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <% include ./footer %>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>